## Usage

```bash
my ai generate module user
my ai generate crud product --fields name:string,price:number
my ai generate service billing --dry-run
```

Programmatic:

```typescript
import { complete, buildModulePrompt } from './src/ai/index.js';

const text = await complete({ prompt: buildModulePrompt('user', 'email:email') });
```

Install via plugin: `my plugin install @mycli/ai`
